summary: a dark link preset for ReaperUnborn
descriptionHtml:
this is my take on a dark link preset as requested by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/35617965]ReaperUnborn[/url]. i wish could have had the skin darker but this is as best as i could get. he is a wood elf
 
Requirements
Apachii sky hair - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?
Brows - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/? 

And thank you to the amazing [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/4538474]JKalenad[/url] for the armor and weapons from the relics of hyrule mod. [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40615/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40615/?[/url]   it is my top favorite mod and i have been using it for a long time
author: littlelee99
